data.description: Fall in love as you walk into this Cape Coral pool home ,this gem offers over 2400 square feet of living space consisting of 4 bedrooms and 3 baths and oversized 2 car garage.  Enjoy in style the huge heated, salted water pool, with marble finishes enjoy the gazebo and the relaxing covered terrace and perfect for gatherings with friends and family.  Excellent location with quick access to restaurants and shops.
